{"tid":492402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方明起加強票控亂過馬路 為期五天","createTime":"2017-12-07T13:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T15:10:41.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fedb0351c6396eaba172f0c319a2b7122596013a","tid":492402,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1084058/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1084058%2F&d=AfAONR5CkOAEVl4rRvlejEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=dfdc1658\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1084058%2F&h=6be8d17a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1084058/</a><br />\n<br />\n警務處將由明日起至12月12日進行為期五天的全港行人道路安全行動，以減少涉及行人，特別是長者及青少年的交通意外。行動期間，警方將加強執法，票控亂過馬路或干犯嚴重交通違例事項的行人。<br />\n<br />\n各警察總區道路安全組人員在行人道路安全行動前，已在全港多個地點派發宣傳單張，加強行人對道路安全的意識及呼籲市民遵守交通規則。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，行人通常違反的規則包括不遵守交通燈號、不使用在其十五米範圍內的行人過路設施橫過馬路，及攀越路邊圍欄或穿過中央分道帶進入車路等。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方數字，今年1月至10月共有2650名行人於交通意外中傷亡，包括55名行人死亡。死者當中，29人為65歲或以上的長者。與去年同期比較，死亡人數減少九人，傷亡人數減少167人，65歲或以上死者則減少八人。"},{"pid":"0313effe4d017f622422c88ed0325ffe7a5def60","tid":492402,"uid":3748,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:34:26.000Z","msg":"市民明起遵守交通規則過馬路 為期五天"},{"pid":"244edbffa75b656f5b17e8431952237402180287","tid":492402,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>市民明起遵守交通規則過馬路 為期五天</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ecb43f9c04231eff4e901687ee24f6b421e183","tid":492402,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>市民明起遵守交通規則過馬路 為期五天</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2bd91abe6524dbc58a9c6dcd9fe5dc05a2fcb8","tid":492402,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>市民明起遵守交通規則過馬路 為期五天</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係五天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f87760569053967519ebad5baac5bb1871aea23","tid":492402,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>市民明起遵守交通規則過馬路 為期五天</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係五天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}